Package: haiDash
Title: Explore Healthcare-Associated Infection Counts with a Shiny Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Qiuyuan",
             family = "Chen",
             role = c("aut","cre"),
             email = "qiuyuan.chen@example.com"))
Description: An example package for ETC5523 Assignment 4. 
    It ships a small cleaned dataset ('hai_clean') derived from BHAI's 
    'num_hai_patients' (Germany, PPS 2011), provides a helper function 
    'summarise_hai()' to compute totals and shares, and exposes a Shiny 
    app via 'run_app()' for interactive exploration.
